data.description: Welcome to Chestnut Lake Estates! Inside this community, you will find this 3 bedroom, 2 and a half bath traditional home waiting to be made yours! An open floor plan on the main, with an eat-in kitchen and new flooring is a plus! HVAC, Water Heater, and Roofing have all been updated! The backyard is spacious and ideal for fun and get-togethers with its very own saltwater pool! Privacy will not be a problem, as the property is fenced in. Come and see why this home should be yours today!!!
